        "meta_description": "Bruce Willis' wife Emma Heming Willis shared a sweet photo on Instagram Thursday of herself and the actor celebrating the holiday with their kids Mabel and Evelyn. Bruce's other daughters Rumer Willis, Scout Willis and Tallulah Willis could also be seen in the snapshot, along with his ex-wife, Demi Moore. They were also joined by Rumer's boyfriend Derek Richard Thomas and Tallulah's partner Jake Miller.",
